<?php $labels=['draft'=>'Draft','counting'=>'Sedang dihitung','review'=>'Ditinjau','completed'=>'Selesai','cancelled'=>'Dibatalkan'];?><header class="page-head"><div><span class="eyebrow">Audit stok</span><h1>Stock opname</h1></div></header><div class="split"><section class="panel"><div class="table-wrap" tabindex="0" aria-label="Daftar stock opname, geser horizontal bila diperlukan"><table><thead><tr><th>Nomor</th><th>Status</th><th>Dibuat oleh</th><th>Aksi</th></tr></thead><tbody><?php foreach($items as $x):?><tr><td><?=e($x['opname_number'])?></td><td><span class="badge"><?=e($labels[$x['status']]??$x['status'])?></span></td><td><?=e($x['creator'])?></td><td><a class="table-action" href="<?=url('/admin/stock-opnames/'.$x['id'])?>">Buka opname</a></td></tr><?php endforeach?><?php if(!$items):?><tr><td colspan="4" class="empty-cell">Belum ada sesi stock opname.</td></tr><?php endif?></tbody></table></div></section><section class="panel sticky"><h2>Mulai sesi baru</h2><p>Stok sistem saat ini akan disimpan sebagai pembanding.</p><form method="post" action="<?=url('/admin/stock-opnames')?>" class="stack"><?=csrf_field()?><label>Catatan sesi<textarea name="notes" placeholder="Contoh: Opname bulanan Juli"></textarea></label><button class="button">Ambil snapshot stok</button></form></section></div>
